<br>
Grim doesn't need to post the numbers in every single thread, he doesn't need to defend that the numbers show that we need work, they do that by themselves.  Grim DOES post that the class needs work, but ISN'T broken.  So, relax, and stop trying to pick fights with one of the most respected players in the wizard community.<br>
